---
# List checkers:
# clang-tidy --list-checks -checks='*' | grep "modernize"

# Here we:
# - Disable all checks
# - Enable the ones that seem reasonable
# - Disable the ones we don't want to obbey (yet)
# clang-diagnostic-*,

